Class MoneyHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.oasp.gastronomy.restaurant.general.common.api.MoneyHelper

  • public final class MoneyHelper
extends Object
    This class is a little helper to deal with Money. It provides convenience methods to get a Money.

      • sumMoneys

        public static Money sumMoneys(List<Money> moneyToSum)
        Sums a list of Moneys. The returned Money has the currency of the Moneys in the given list. If the list is empty the ZERO_MONEY is returned.
        Parameters:
        moneyToSum - list of Moneys to sum
        Returns:
        sum of given Moneys, ZERO_MONEY if list is empty
